rows.label: qev031502_MSG0001
rows.name:
Beasts will be on us soon. We intercept at your word.
Are you ready?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Oche that you are ready to go.

rows.label: qev031502_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that you need a little more time.

rows.label: qev031502_MSG0002
rows.name: Show us why Ganglion fears you, Earth alien![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG0003
rows.name: We will show Cavern woman she is not needed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG0004
rows.name:
We face massive flood of beasts.
Be sure you are fully prepared.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG1001
rows.name:
Slovity Pagus fights with strength. With honor.
Even in Tree Clan, few can rival her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG1002
rows.name: ...Not that Cavern thug can ever earn respect![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG1003
rows.name:
I will defeat her one day. Prove glory of Tree Clan.
This truce is temporary![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG0005
rows.name: Beasts are nearly upon us. BLADEs beg us to flee.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031502_MSG0006
rows.name: They should fight harder. Then we won't need to run![ST:wait ]
